high_descs: Walk ahead to the right side of the table and face it.
Pick up the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn left and veer right to the fridge.
Place the bread on the top right shelf of the fridge. Close the door, wait a moment, and take the bread out again.
Turn left and walk to the stove.
Place the bread on the counter to the right of the stove, all the way in the back right corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled loaf of bread on a counter.

high_descs: Turn right and forward before facing to your left at the side of the table
Pick up a loaf of bread
Turn left, right and then turn to your left again so that you are facing the fridge
Put the loaf of bread in the fridge and chill it for a few seconds before taking it out
Head to your left and face the front of the oven
Put the loaf of bread down on the right hand side counter
anns.task_desc: Chill a loaf of bread and set it down

high_descs: Turn right and take a step then turn left and walk to the wall then turn left.
Pick up the loaf of bread that's near the wall.
Turn left and walk past the table on your right then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the bread in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk over to the stove that's to your right in front of you.
Put  the cold loaf of bread to the right of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold loaf of bread on the counter.
